    <briefdescription>
<para>The settings ITS store module API. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The functions declared in this header allow customization of the settings implementation of the ITS store module. They are not meant to be called directly other than by the settings ITS store module. This header file may and must be included when providing a custom implementation of one or more of these functions (<computeroutput>CONFIG_SECURE_STORAGE_ITS_STORE_SETTINGS_*_CUSTOM</computeroutput>). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
